SafeCellsLeft, DEC 256
TotalMines, DEC 0
BoardData, DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
           DEC 0
